<div style="width:0;height:0;clear:both"></div><dl class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-">
<dd class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-title">
<h1 >南北差异</h1>
<a href="javascript:;" class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" href="javascript:;" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=512472" target="_blank" class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" nslog-type="90000102"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num"></span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">南北差异是指我国南方北方之间的差异。由于我国南北双方所处的地理位置、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99">气候</a>特征、历史文化、风俗习惯以及政治经济活动等方面的不同，造成了我国南北方自然景观和人文景观的显著差异。</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div id="hotspotmining_s" class="clearfix" alog-alias="hotspotmining-subLemma-">
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="hotspotmining" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><ul class="hotspotminingNavbar clearfix">
<li class="active" data-id="457845">TA说</li>
</ul>
<div id="hotspotminingContent-457845" class="hotspotminingContent clearfix showPic" style="display: block">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_pic ">
<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=1fc9491353a89a1d62aa3988" target="_blank"><img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/whfpf%3D360%2C280%2C50/sign=036372c7d8ca7bcb7d2e946fd8345855/b219ebc4b74543a9f34bb1c811178a82b9011465.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit"><span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tit"><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=1fc9491353a89a1d62aa3988" target="_blank">中国南北方，到底有什么不同？</a></span><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/flag_new_5f5180c.png" />
<span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tim">2019-10-08 10:10</span>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_cnt">
<span>中国有960万平方千米的陆地，和300万平方千米的海洋，在如此广袤辽阔的疆土上，地域差异将是永恒的话题，而其中最为人津津乐道的，莫过于南北差异</span><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=1fc9491353a89a1d62aa3988" target="_blank">...详情</a></div>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_rel ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_rel_tit">相关新闻</div>
<ul class="hotspotminingContent_rel_cnt">
</ul>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_web">内容来自<img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/logo_tashuo_274a010.png"></div>
</div>
</div>
