<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
南方人：我来了北方，从此没有了夜生活
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=6a0cd5ee22136544038895a5&lemmaId=512472&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
晚上11点走在北方和南方城市的街头，你会有不同的感受：一个非常安静，一个热闹非凡。多少南方人来了北方才发现，晚上连个能吃宵夜的地方都没有。为什么南方夜生活那么丰富，而北方人很早就洗洗睡了？视知TV带你解密</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-08-09</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">74</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="1fc9491353a89a1d62aa3988">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=e5dede4b&authorId=b990360add38135a452ace21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/9a504fc2d562853511f860359cef76c6a7ef638e.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>星球研究所</strong>
<span>探索极致风光的地理控</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=1fc9491353a89a1d62aa3988&lemmaId=512472&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/b3b7d0a20cf431add8c226174436acaf2edd988f.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
中国南北方，到底有什么不同？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=1fc9491353a89a1d62aa3988&lemmaId=512472&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
中国有960万平方千米的陆地，和300万平方千米的海洋，在如此广袤辽阔的疆土上，地域差异将是永恒的话题，而其中最为人津津乐道的，莫过于南北差异</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-09-07</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">58</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="5bb6134ffc6116d8d14f1da4">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=963ee254&authorId=f483ebd1482366d63610c620&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/9922720e0cf3d7cae17997e2f81fbe096a63a993.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>视知TV</strong>
<span>聚焦人文历史领域有知有趣的知识</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=5bb6134ffc6116d8d14f1da4&lemmaId=512472&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/d1160924ab18972b24ead100eacd7b899f510a2c.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
为了研究中国南北方人有啥不同，有个外国人在星巴克摆了把椅子
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=5bb6134ffc6116d8d14f1da4&lemmaId=512472&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
在咖啡馆的过道上被一把椅子挡住了路，你会选择挪开还是绕开？不要觉得这是个简单的问题，因为从答案中可以看出你是南方人还是北方人。南北方人的思维有何不同？南北方的差异因何而生？视知TV来和大家探讨一下。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-08-07</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">45</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="slider-item">
<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="24921b1a0d2186e07289d996">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=915cb961&authorId=0705d7139a9e0dfd71a20723&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/d1a20cf431adcbefff7397d6a2af2edda2cc9f9f.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>印客美学</strong>
<span>一个讲段子的艺术美学号</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=24921b1a0d2186e07289d996&lemmaId=512472&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/838ba61ea8d3fd1f3745b92c3f4e251f95ca5f53.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
南方和北方也太太太太不一样了吧
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=24921b1a0d2186e07289d996&lemmaId=512472&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
其原因是南方气候湿润，降水丰富，地表河网密布，因此为适应"水乡"的船舶运输便应运而生。
而北方多干旱、半干旱气候，草场广布，畜牧业发达，马匹除了提供乳肉产品外，又以其耐力好、速度快而被北方人民驯化为代步工具，成为北方大地的交通工具。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-09-16</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">6</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul></div>
<div class="tashuo-bottom-pager"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
